# NOTE: the repo-global binaries/ tree (vendored wheels + sd-cli) is
# intentionally NOT excluded. uv reads the metadata of every
# [tool.uv.sources] path dependency during `uv sync`, even ones whose platform
# marker excludes the current OS, so every vendored wheel must be in the image
# or the linux/aarch64 sync aborts.
# Per-extension model-download caches under */binaries/ are excluded:
**/binaries/huggingface
**/binaries/download
